         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Column I:;Through Aion son of Sarapion;Elias  tal. 6,550;Aion son of Sarapion  tal. 45,200;Heras son of Sarapion  tal. 8,300;Sokrates  tal. 24,600;Leein  tal. 1,600;Amatas  tal. 19,500 (cancelled);Atolas  tal. 400;   Total, tal. 106,250;    tal. 86,650;Aion son of Sarapion, receiver;Aion [     ];Tamaleis [     ];Atisis [     ];Heras son of Sarapion  tal. 780;Termou[thion  tal.] 6,400;Nilammon  tal. 30,100.;Column II:;In the name of Kollouthes,;through Tapaeis  tal. 9,300;And for the name of Heras  tal. 1,250;Likewise Tapaeis for the two names  tal. 10,600;Receipts of Aion son of Sarapion:;Titoueis  tal. 50,850;Pankratis  tal. 14,216;Heras son of Sarapion  tal. 5,400;Heras son of Hol  tal. 3,700;Total  tal. 70,500. Another  tal. 3,700.</ab>
